{"tid":1404600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實藍絲係可以唔等於撐警","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T08:05:10.000Z","uid":92255,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a90d0108c5a1af1e53ae71e08e5a4ef07048fd7a","tid":1404600,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"大家好容易墮入一個陷阱，就係&quot;黃藍&quot;一定要對立。<br />\n<br />\n所以當黃絲要成立警察獨立調查委員會嘅時候，大部分藍絲就覺得呢個一定係錯，因為同佢立場對立嘅事，一定係錯。<br />\n<br />\n但其實支持警察已經唔關黃絲定係藍絲事，而係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 道德問題！ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個正常人見到啲警察咁樣對待市民，都唔應該去支持。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯！警察係應該執法，但係當佢已經<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 濫用佢哋嘅權力嘅時候 </span></span>，咁就一定唔啱！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家同藍絲傾計嘅時候，可以同佢哋講佢哋可以有自己嘅立場，而且撐警亦都唔係捆綁住藍絲所守護嘅嘢，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 支持送中 </strong></span></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong> 撐警 </strong></span></span>兩樣嘢可以分開。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家！"},{"pid":"bee1fc5742a70fc3a7b0e1c0c296ea4dbe9a6e11","tid":1404600,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df3f5ad6dde024576cdf8071550e9b58b8cf5440","tid":1404600,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6198076bef31f624838ab43fe764a92e54bce190","tid":1404600,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保家衛國</span></span>"},{"pid":"55221f1eca7375d9281f83ec862ca9922391997a","tid":1404600,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:30:29.000Z","msg